# Local runtime/state data and generated QA artifacts
# Ignore local runtime/generated data, but TRACK the hand-curated Finviz
# sector/industry taxonomy the SPX heatmap loader depends on (data/* + negation,
# because a plain `data/` exclusion can't be re-included file-by-file).
data/*
!data/finviz-classification.json
!data/heatmap-classification-auto.json
artifacts/
output/
.claude/
.tmp*
qa-*.png
dev-server.*.log
rubicon-server.*.log
qa-server.*.log
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.bak-*

# Secrets and machine-local environment
.env
.env.*
.secrets/
*.pem
*.key

